<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/search.php?query=%28%28subject%3A%22Sartori%2C%20Giovanni%22%20OR%20subject%3A%22Giovanni%20Sartori%22%20OR%20creator%3A%22Sartori%2C%20Giovanni%22%20OR%20creator%3A%22Giovanni%20Sartori%22%20OR%20creator%3A%22Sartori%2C%20G%2E%22%20OR%20title%3A%22Giovanni%20Sartori%22%20OR%20description%3A%22Sartori%2C%20Giovanni%22%20OR%20description%3A%22Giovanni%20Sartori%22%29%20OR%20%28%221924-2017%22%20AND%20Sartori%29%29%20AND%20%28-mediatype:software%29">Works by or about Giovanni Sartori</a> at the <a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a>
